# Environment Variables Template

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in the actual values.

## Application

```
APP_NAME=Bowling-HQ
APP_VERSION=1.0.0
DEBUG=False
ENVIRONMENT=development
```

## Database - PostgreSQL

```
POSTGRES_USER=postgres
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=your_secure_password
POSTGRES_DB=bowling_hq
POSTGRES_HOST=localhost
POSTGRES_PORT=5432
```

## Database - MongoDB

```
MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017
MONGODB_DB=bowling_hq
```

## Database - Redis

```
REDIS_HOST=localhost
REDIS_PORT=6379
REDIS_DB=0
REDIS_PASSWORD=
```

## API Configuration

```
API_HOST=localhost
API_PORT=8000
API_PREFIX=/api/v1
CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:5173
```

## Frontend Configuration

```
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000/api/v1
VITE_APP_NAME=Bowling-HQ
```

## Security

```
SECRET_KEY=your_secret_key_here
ALGORITHM=HS256
ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=30
```

## Logging

```
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
LOG_FORMAT=json
```

## Features (Toggle for Phase progression)

```
ENABLE_COMMANDER_AI=True
ENABLE_GHOST_BOWLER=True
ENABLE_SESSIONS=False
ENABLE_VIDEO_COACH=False
ENABLE_DIGITAL_TWIN=False
```